column5: If anybody wants to talk boats, fishing...or even better, to buy a boat... I'll be working the boat sale at the new Cabela's in Edmonton this weekend. Stop by and say Hello! Terry
Does that mean you might be having something to do with the new Cabela's opening in Saskatoon later this spring??

I would stop in and bs but i dislike that store!!!! Its for hunters and not fisherman. I am gonna check out the boat show though, Even though i got one on order.Very lack of fish hooks at Edmonton cabelas.
do you have a schedule of when you will be there
Good to meet you, LIR. Good fishing to you, this summer!
